metadata.name: The Phycodurus
metadata.description:
The Phycodurus is an elusive creature that roams the arenaceous region of Centuria. They have an acute vision, but as they learn to fly, they lose their sight.

Riders of the Phycodurus are scarce, but they can train the beasts to hover the dry land at incredible speed.
